cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "nirs4all-lite"
abstract: >-
  A portable aggregate distribution (Rust core + Python/R/MATLAB/Octave/JS-WASM bindings) that
  re-exports dag-ml, dag-ml-data, nirs4all-formats, nirs4all-io, nirs4all-datasets, and
  nirs4all-methods without adding new parsers or methods. (Being renamed to nirs4all-core.)
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Beurier
    given-names: Gregory
    email: beurier@cirad.fr
    affiliation: CIRAD
repository-code: "https://github.com/GBeurier/nirs4all-lite"
url: "https://nirs4all.org"
license:
  - CECILL-2.1
  - AGPL-3.0-or-later
version: "0.2.0"
keywords:
  - NIRS
  - spectroscopy
  - chemometrics
  - rust
  - wasm
  - bindings
